The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Javier B., Appellant.

— Judgment, Supreme Court, Bronx County (Murray Koenig, J.), rendered on June 30,1981, unanimously affirmed. The order of this court entered on July 3, 1984 is recalled and vacated. No opinion. Concur — Sandler, J. P., Ross, Carro, Silverman and Alexander, JJ.
